scussion of future RSMA research challenges is also\nprovided to inspire future research on RSMA-aided wireless communication for\nbeyond 5G systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 Jan 2022 07:13:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 25 Jul 2022 16:53:19 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 30 Sep 2022 11:33:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-03"}
