 and sufficient condition for convexity\nof the smooth part of the objective function is studied. Numerical examples\nshow the efficacy of LiMES in applications to sparse modeling and robust\nregression.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 Jan 2022 09:37:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 1 Apr 2023 13:09:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-04"}
