ucture of a prototypical lifex application and to provide them\nwith a possible approach to include the generated cardiac fibers into more\nsophisticated computational pipelines.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 Jan 2022 12:08:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 11 Jan 2022 02:06:04 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 23 Jan 2022 12:28:00 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 7 Oct 2022 10:31:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-10"}
