f the\nlead concentration in a sample of water. This paper reports on the\ninstrumentation challenges of developing the electronics for the PlomBOX and on\nthe first prototype.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 Jan 2022 14:03:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-11"}
