ides with the intracellular medium and\nextracellular one, which are two inter-penetrating and superimposed continua\nconnected at each point by the cardiac cellular membrane. The interest of the\nproposed method comes from the fact that it combines microscopic and mesoscopic\ncharacteristics to obtain a macroscopic description of the electrical behavior\nof the heart.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 Jan 2022 15:50:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-11"}
