srupted conditions of the local\nvasculature. This results in a noticeable effect of heat on hypoxic cells.\nAdditionally, when pronounced cell death occurs, it is followed by a\nsignificant increase in the oxygen levels.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 Jan 2022 13:24:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-28"}
